Source: duckdb-fdw
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~), postgresql-server-dev-all, postgresql-18-pg-duckdb (>= 1.1.1) | postgresql-17-pg-duckdb (>= 1.1.1) | postgresql-16-pg-duckdb (>= 1.1.1) | postgresql-15-pg-duckdb (>= 1.1.1) | postgresql-14-pg-duckdb (>= 1.1.1)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/alitrack/duckdb_fdw

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-duckdb-fdw
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-duckdb-fdw
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-duckdb (>= 1.1.1)
Description: DuckDB Foreign data wrapper extension for PostgreSQL PGVERSION
  This is a foreign data wrapper (FDW) to connect PostgreSQL to DuckDB database file.
  This FDW is built from the duckdb_fdw snapshot at 870bc43 against the DuckDB
  1.4.3 headers and libduckdb.so shipped by postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-duckdb.
